# ⚙️ Usage Pattern (for Agent System)

```yaml
agent_system:
  orchestrator:
    role: task_router

  agents:
    - name: research_agent
      use: Research Agent

    - name: trading_agent
      use: Finance / Trading Agent

    - name: content_agent
      use: Content Automation Agent

    - name: dev_agent
      use: Dev / Infra Agent
```

---

# ✅ 設計原則

* 每個 Agent = 一個明確職能
* 每個 Agent 對應一組 GitHub tools
* 支援：

  * multi-agent orchestration
  * tool calling
  * RAG indexing
  * skill loading
